snippet.title: Angry Birds 2 – Bigger. Badder. Birdier. (Official Launch Trailer)
snippet.description:
It just got real. The pigs have gone and gaffled the eggs once again, and it’s up to our flock of furious fowl to get them back. Time to storm the beach!

Download Angry Birds 2 from the Apple App Store or Google Play now and join the fight: http://rov.io/PlayAB2_yt

P.S. No pigs were harmed in the making of this film. Oink!
